						<msItem n="2" defective="false" class="embr pres">
							<title type="supplied">Embættisbréf <name type="person" key="JonHal013">Jóns Hallsonar</name></title>
							<note><p>Embættisbréf Jóns Hallsonar sóknarprests til Fells og Höfða, skrifað af <name type="person" key="ThoHop001">Thorkil Hoppe</name> stiftamtmanni, dagsett <date when="1842-05-18">18. maí 1842</date>.</p></note>							
						</msItem>
						
						<msItem n="3" defective="false" class="embr pres">
							<title type="supplied">Embættisbréf <name type="person" key="JonHal013">Jóns Hallsonar</name></title>
							<note><p>Embættisbréf Jóns Hallsonar prófasts í Skagafjarðarsýslu, skrifað af <name type="person" key="HelTho001">Helga Thordersen</name> biskupi, dagsett <date when="1851-11-12">12. nóvember 1851</date>.</p></note>							
						</msItem>
						<msItem n="4" defective="false" class="embr">
