						</msItem>
						<msItem n="5" defective="false" class="embr jarbr">
							<title type="supplied">Embættisbréf vegna <placeName key="ReySta06">Reynistaðar</placeName></title>
							<note><p>Embættisbréf <name type="person" key="BjaTho003">Bjarna Vigfússonar Thorarensens</name> til <name type="person" key="EinSte001">Einars Stefánssonar</name> vegna Reynistaðar <date when="1836-12-28">28. desember 1836</date>.</p></note>							
